Have you ever tried to extract content from a document but didn’t know where to start? Join Platform Engineer Amanda Winkles as she walks through how GenAI can help make reviewing contracts and extracting content for clients much easier. By using LLMs like Granite-13b-chat and Mistral Large to extract data from contracts, you’ll be able to build and apply a content extraction solution to help sift through your larger documents.
